
                         LaoTu 


    ~ How do I run this?

      1. Make sure the database path in laotu.py is appropriate for your OS 

      2. install the app from the root of the project directory

         pip install --editable .

      3. tell flask about the right application (if windows, use set instead of export):

         export FLASK_APP=laotu
         export PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_haUn12yj5cA394KQK37hzh
         export SECRET_KEY=sk_test_52QkxEpzwiy1p4bNKTX18Vy7

      4. fire up a shell and run this:

         flask initdb

      5. now you can run minitwit:

         flask run

         the application will greet you on
         http://localhost:5000/


         Tests:
         
        Run the `python setup.py test` file to
            see the tests pass.

            
         